    <p style="color:var(--foreground);opacity:.85;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">Lume works, but the marketing overpromises. It's a decent aluminum-free option for everyday odor control, especially for sensitive skin. But the cream format, polarizing scents, and exaggerated duration claims push it into overhyped territory.</p>
